The course offers and overview of the situation of young people 
at risk of exclusion, including those who are not studying or working (NEETS) both in Estonia and globally. The topics covered in the course are closely tied to preventing school dropout and discontinuation of education. At the core of preventive activities in this course is the development of self-directed learning skills to support the continuation of the learning path for young people at risk of exclusion.Objectives/eesmärkid:  xxxLearning outcomes/õpiväljund:  xxx
